{"id": "1181659605026209802", "channel_id": "1181659605026209802", "type": 0, "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "author_bot": false, "content": "已經回報兩次了，目前仍未修復，但也沒有在未修復的已知問題處看到，遂回報第三次。\n\n詳細狀況請看下面影片。\n機型為Nokia X30 5G\nUID100030369\n資源修復與關機重開均無效。", "timestamp": "2023-12-05T18:13:24.012000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-12-05T18:14:49.885000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1181659965912514650", "filename": "az_recorder_20231202_061039.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 14169461, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1181659605026209802/1181659965912514650/az_recorder_20231202_061039.mp4?ex=6a00cb1a&is=69ff799a&hm=9b44e5ca8244d130d9c39d8a06163e638d0d4ea0c7ed4422007c4dd5c3143d86&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1181659605026209802", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」登入動畫與抽卡動畫異常", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1181465105024684072", "channel_id": "1181465105024684072", "type": 0, "author_id": "451726402488631306", "author_name": "rainbowteemo", "author_bot": false, "content": "或許可以把關卡的星星當成難度，三星就是目前的難度，然後每少一顆星就降低一點難度\n也不需要太麻煩全部數值都重新調整，給個降低難度的特殊造物就行\n這樣想挑戰極限的人也是能正常玩，沒那麼強的人也能少拿一點獎勵看劇情之類的", "timestamp": "2023-12-05T05:20:31.598000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1181465105024684072", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」一點降低遊戲難度但不會影響到目前遊玩的建議", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
